{"name":"Debilitating Barrage","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Upon reaching 17th level, you've gained the knowledge to temporarily lower a creature's fortitude by striking a series of pressure points. Whenever you hit a single creature with three or more attacks in one round, you can spend 3 ki points to cause the creature to suffer a vulnerability to a damage type of your choice for 1 minute, or until after they take any damage of that type.</p><p>Creatures with resistance or immunity to the chosen damage type do not suffer vulnerability. Instead, their resistance to the chosen damage type is lost for the duration, or their immunity is reduced to resistance for the duration. </p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TDCS","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Monk 17 (Cobalt Soul)","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"subclassFeature","source":"TalDorei","hash":"debilitating%20barrage_monk_phb_cobalt%20soul_taldorei_17_taldorei","propDroppable":"subclassFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"6c2d5182165e37f68061ed2d8ccb76804d6652ff"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004192478,"modifiedTime":1682004192478,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"DtGMMRNbZh4hsvst"}
{"name":"Unarmored Movement improvement","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>At 9th level, you gain the ability to move along vertical surfaces and across liquids on your turn without falling during the move.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"flat"},"requirements":"Monk 9","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/mighty-force.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"PHB","hash":"unarmored%20movement%20improvement_monk_phb_9_phb","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"cb8b8739e675a1cb580866864701a88ff2695a54"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004194657,"modifiedTime":1682004194657,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"EVGlcPilFyCb039L"}
{"name":"Step of the Wind","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You can spend 1 ki point to take the @action[Disengage] or @action[Dash] action as a bonus action on your turn, and your jump distance is doubled for the turn.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB","activation":{"type":"bonus","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":null,"type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null,"recovery":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Monk 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"classFeature","source":"PHB","hash":"step%20of%20the%20wind_monk_phb_2_phb","propDroppable":"classFeature"},"scene-packer":{"sourceId":"Item.","hash":"4a1baf8a800d40e2910d8e631f43165d42d7bb64"}},"img":"icons/magic/air/air-wave-gust-blue.webp","_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1682004194286,"modifiedTime":1682004194286,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"EpkOtM3h5eHbaTCA"}
